content:
Keep your contact center running if the Omni-Channel routing service becomes unavailable. With Fallback Mode enabled, externally routed work continues to be delivered to agents. For example, your telephony provider continues to route voice calls. Fallback Mode supports Enhanced Omni-Channel only.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer editions.

How: To enable Fallback Mode, log a case with Salesforce Customer Support.
title: Keep Routing Work During Service Degradation
